nodes.text: Dommu was a male Zabrak who lived during the Cold War. Dommu owned a shop in the Senate Commercial District of Coruscant, where he sold item modifications and upgrades.

Dommu appeared in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as a Mods Vendor for Republic players on Coruscant. With the release of Game Update 4.0 on October 20, 2015, Dommu was removed from the game along with the rest of the Mods Vendors. His position is also marked on a map in Star Wars: The Old Republic Explorer's Guide, a game guide released by Prima Games.
